# Build artifacts inside docs/ are preserved by scripts/prepare-pages-dir.mjs.
# Hand-authored docs (docs/adr/, docs/architecture.md, docs/postmortem.md,
# docs/privacy.md, docs/data.md) are NOT ignored — Pages serves them too.
# The Vite build emits docs/index.html, docs/404.html, docs/assets/*,
# docs/version.json — those are committed as part of `chore: publish pages build`.
